\c 6
\s Intshumayelo yentabeni iyaqhubeka. Ukwenza ukulunga
\p
\v 1 Qaphelani ukuthi umsebenzi wenu womusa\f + \fk umsebenzi wenu womusa: \ft kumbe, \fq ukulunga\f* lingawenzi phambi kwabantu ukuze libonwe yibo\f + \fk yibo: \ft or, \fq labo\f*; nxa kunge\add njalo\add*, alilamvuzo kuYihlo osemazulwini.
\v 2 Ngakho nxa usenza umsebenzi womusa, ungakhalisi uphondo phambi kwakho\x + 1 Kor. 15.52. Isam. 8.6,7,8,10,12,13; 9.1,13; 10.7; 11.15. Mat. 23.5. Roma 12.8.\x*, njengokwenza kwabazenzisi emasinagogeni lezindleleni, ukuze badunyiswe ngabantu; ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Sebewemukele umvuzo\x + Luka 6.24. Fil. 4.18.\x* wabo\x + 6.15,16.\x*.
\v 3 Kodwa wena nxa usenza umsebenzi womusa \add isandla\add* sakho sokhohlo kasingakwazi esikwenzayo esokunene sakho,
\v 4 ukuze umsebenzi wakho womusa ube sekusithekeni; njalo uYihlo obona ekusithekeni, yena uzakuvuza obala\x + 6.6,18. Luka 14.14.\x*.
\p
\v 5 Lalapho likhuleka, lingabi njengabazenzisi, ngoba bathanda ukukhuleka bemi emasinagogeni lemahlanganweni endlela, ukuze babonwe ngabantu; ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Sebewemukele umvuzo wabo\x + 6.15,16.\x*.
\v 6 Kodwa wena nxa ukhuleka, ngena\x + 2 Kho. 4.33.\x* endlini yakho yensitha, ubusuvala umnyango wakho, ukhuleke kuYihlo osensitha\x + 24.26. Luka 12.3,24.\x*; njalo uYihlo obona ekusithekeni uzakuvuza obala\x + 6.6,18. Luka 14.14.\x*.
\v 7 Njalo uba likhuleka lingathemelezi\x + Tshu. 5.2.\x* njengabezizwe; ngoba bacabanga ukuthi bazakuzwiwa\x + 18.17. Tshu. 7.14.\x* ngokukhuluma kwabo okunengi\x + 1 Kho. 18.26,29.\x*.
\v 8 Ngakho lingafanani labo; ngoba uYihlo uyakwazi elikuswelayo, lingakaceli kuye\x + 6.32.\x*.
\s UJesu ufundisa ngokukhuleka
\p
\v 9 Ngakho lina khulekani ngokunje: Baba wethu osemazulwini\x + Luka 11.2-4. Mat. 7.11.\x*, kalihlonitshwe ibizo lakho\x + Isa. 29.23. 1 Pet. 3.15.\x*;
\v 10 umbuso wakho kawuze\x + 3.2.\x*; intando yakho kayenziwe\x + 26.39,42. Seb. 21.14.\x*, lemhlabeni njengezulwini\x + Hlab. 103.20,21.\x*;
\v 11 siphe lamuhla ukudla kwethu kwensuku zonke\x + Zaga 30.8.\x*;
\v 12 njalo usithethelele amacala ethu, njengalokhu lathi sibathethelela abalamacala kithi\x + Roma 4.4. Mat. 18.21-35.\x*;
\v 13 njalo ungasingenisi ekulingweni\x + 26.41. Mark. 14.38. Luka 22.40,46.\x*, kodwa usikhulule ebubini\x + 13.19,38. Joha. 17.15. 1 Joha. 2.13,14; 3.12.\x*. Ngoba umbuso ungowakho lamandla lenkazimulo kuze kube nini lanini. Ameni\x + 1 Lan. 29.11; 2 Lan. 20.6.\x*.
\v 14 Ngoba uba lithethelela abantu iziphambeko zabo, uYihlo osezulwini uzalithethelela lani\x + Mark. 11.25,26. Efe. 4.32. Kol. 3.13.\x*.
\v 15 Kodwa uba lingathetheleli abantu iziphambeko zabo, loYihlo kayikulithethelela iziphambeko zenu\x + Jak. 2.13.\x*.
\s Ukuzila ukudla
\p
\v 16 Futhi nxa lizila ukudla\x + Isa. 58.5. Mat. 17.21.\x*, lingabi lobuso obudanileyo njengabazenzisi; ngoba benyukumalisa ubuso babo, ukuze babonakale ebantwini ukuthi bazilile\x + Luka 24.17.\x*; ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Sebewemukele umvuzo wabo\x + 6.15,16.\x*.
\v 17 Kodwa wena nxa uzila ukudla, gcoba ikhanda lakho, ugeze ubuso bakho\x + 2 Sam. 12.20. Dan. 10.3. 2 Lan. 28.15.\x*,
\v 18 ukuze ungabonakali ebantwini ukuthi uzilile ukudla, kodwa kuYihlo osekusithekeni; njalo uYihlo obona ekusithekeni uzakuvuza obala\x + 6.6,18. Luka 14.14.\x*.
\s Inotho eqotho lokukhanya okuqotho
\p
\v 19 Lingazibekeli impahla eziligugu emhlabeni\x + Zaga 23.4.\x*, lapho inundu lokuthomba okona khona, lalapho amasela afohlela khona ebe;
\v 20 kodwa zibekeleni izinto eziligugu ezulwini, lapho inundu lokuthomba okungoni khona\x + 6.20. Luka 12.33. Isa. 50.9; 51.8.\x*, lalapho amasela angafohleli khona ebe\x + 6.20. 24.43. Luka 12.39. Jobe 24.16.\x*.
\v 21 Ngoba lapho okukhona impahla yenu eligugu, lenhliziyo yenu izakuba lapho.
\v 22 Isibane somzimba yilihlo\x + 6.22,23. Luka 11.34,35.\x*; ngakho uba ilihlo lakho liphilile, umzimba wakho wonke uzagcwala ukukhanya\x + 20.15. Mark. 7.22. Dute. 15.9.\x*;
\v 23 kodwa uba ilihlo lakho lilibi, umzimba wakho wonke uzakuba lobumnyama\x + 20.15. Mark. 7.22. Dute. 15.9.\x*. Ngakho uba ukukhanya okuphakathi kwakho kuyibumnyama, umnyama mkhulu kangakanani\x + Jobe 38.15.\x*!
\p
\v 24 Kakho ongakhonza amakhosi amabili; ngoba uzazonda enye, athande enye; kumbe uzabambelela kwenye, adelele enye\x + Luka 16.13. Josh. 24.19.\x*. Lingekhonze uNkulunkulu\x + Gal. 1.10. Jak. 4.4. 1 Joha. 2.15.\x* \w loMamona\w**\x + Luka 16.9,11,13.\x*.
\s Ukukhathazeka, lokuthemba kuNkulunkulu
\p
\v 25 Ngakho ngithi kini\x + Luka 12.22-31.\x*: Lingaphisekeli impilo yenu, ukuthi lizakudlani lokuthi lizanathani; lomzimba wenu, ukuthi lizakwembathani. Impilo kayidluli yini ukudla, lomzimba izembatho\x + 6.27,28,31,34. 1 Sam. 9.5. Hlab. 55.22. Fil. 4.6. Heb. 13.5. 1 Pet. 5.7.\x*?
\v 26 Khangelani inyoni zezulu, ukuthi kazihlanyeli njalo kazivuni, kazibutheli eziphaleni; kanti uYihlo osezulwini uyazondla; lina kalizidluli kakhulu yini\x + Jobe 38.41.\x*?
\v 27 Njalo nguwuphi kini ngokuphisekela ongengezelela ingalo ibenye ebudeni bakhe\x + Hlab. 39.5. Luka 12.26.\x*?
\v 28 Langezembatho liphisekelani? Qaphelisani imiduze yeganga, ukuthi ikhula njani; kayitshikatshiki, kayiphothi;
\v 29 kodwa ngithi kini: LoSolomoni ebucwazicwazini bakhe bonke wayengembathiswanga njengomunye wayo\x + 1 Kho. 10.4-7.\x*.
\v 30 Njalo uba uNkulunkulu esembathisa ngokunjalo utshani beganga, obukhona lamuhla, kuthi kusasa buphoswe eziko, kayikule\add mbathisa\add* kakhulu yini, lina abokholo oluncinyane?
\v 31 Ngakho lingaphisekeli \add lutho\add*, lisithi: Sizakudlani? Kumbe: Sizanathani? Loba: Sizakwembathani\x + 8.26; 14.31; 16.8. Luka 12.28.\x*?
\v 32 Ngoba zonke lezizinto izizwe ziyazidinga; ngoba uYihlo osezulwini uyazi ukuthi liyaziswela zonke lezizinto\x + 6.8.\x*.
\v 33 Kodwa dingani kuqala umbuso kaNkulunkulu lokulunga kwakhe, njalo zonke lezizinto zizakwengezelelwa kini\x + 1 Kho. 3.11-14. Hlab. 37.25. Mark. 10.30. 1 Tim. 4.8.\x*.
\v 34 Ngakho lingaphisekeli ikusasa; ngoba ikusasa izaziphisekela yona; bulwanele usuku obalo ububi\x + 6.27,28,31,34. 1 Sam. 9.5. Hlab. 55.22. Fil. 4.6. Heb. 13.5. 1 Pet. 5.7.\x*.